<h3>Info_page</h3>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Botanical Guide</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        header .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        header nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }

        header nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        main {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 25%;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .sidebar .plant {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .sidebar .plant.active {
            border-color: black;
            background-color: #000;
            color: white;
        }

        .sidebar .plant img {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }

        .content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 2rem;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .content h1 {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content .details {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .content .details div {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .content .details div img {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .content .description {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">Blossom Logo</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#">My Garden</a>
            <a href="#">Botanical Guide</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="plant active">
                <img src="plant-icon.png" alt="Snake Plant">
                <div>
                    <div>Snake Plant</div>
                    <small>Sansevieria</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plant">
                <img src="plant-icon.png" alt="Spider Plant">
                <div>
                    <div>Spider Plant</div>
                    <small>Chlorophytum comosum</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plant">
                <img src="plant-icon.png" alt="Monstera">
                <div>
                    <div>Monstera</div>
                    <small>Monstera deliciosa</small>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="plant">
                <img src="plant-icon.png" alt="Aloe Vera">
                <div>
                    <div>Aloe Vera</div>
                    <small>Aloe barbadensis miller</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>
        <section class="content">
            <h1>Snake Plant</h1>
            <h2>Sansevieria</h2>
            <div class="details">
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-care.png" alt="Care">
                    <span>Care Level: Low-maintenance</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-environment.png" alt="Environment">
                    <span>Environment: Indoor</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-light.png" alt="Light">
                    <span>Light: Low to bright indirect light; very adaptable</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-water.png" alt="Water">
                    <span>Water: Sparingly, allow soil to dry out completely between waterings</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-temperature.png" alt="Temperature">
                    <span>Temperature: Average indoor temperatures; tolerates a wide range</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-growth.png" alt="Growth">
                    <span>Growth Rate: Slow to moderate</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img src="icon-benefits.png" alt="Benefits">
                    <span>Benefits: Known for purifying air by removing toxins</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="description">
                <p>Snake plants are well-known for their resilience and adaptability...</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>


